ated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\",\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:28:    \"description\" : \"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\",\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:46:    \"description\" : \"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-starter/index.json:4:    \"reason\": \"The published JAR for org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter:2.6.3 contains only META-INF files and no JVM class files; it is a dependency starter whose runtime classes are supplied by its dependencies.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-starter-validation/index.json:4:    \"reason\": \"The published JAR for org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-validation:3.4.3 contains only META-INF files and no JVM class files; it is a dependency starter whose runtime classes are supplied by its dependencies.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-starter-data-jdbc/index.json:4:    \"reason\": \"The published spring-boot-starter-data-jdbc-4.0.6 JAR contains only META-INF/MANIFEST.MF, LICENSE.txt, and NOTICE.txt and no JVM class files; it is a dependency starter whose runtime classes are supplied by dependencies.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-starter-web/index.json:4: