rationException` from `System.setSecurityManager` on newer JDKs.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"JDK 25 may reject or disable SecurityManager installation; tests that require a live SecurityManager can fail even though normal OGNL expression coverage is reachable.\",\n    \"Native Image verification remains authoritative for whether Javassist-backed expression compilation must be guarded or limited in runtime assertions.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_031e7fa3a7a1e1b6016a3f999e811881969a9b8160cc443212\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1853, "output": 775, "cacheRead": 51712, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 54340, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782552974732, "responseId": "resp_031e7fa3a7a1e1b6016a3f998f585c8196bcf3b9fe2a4131f7"}, "toolResults": []}
